'''octane'''

#{{chemistry}} Any of the [[isomeric]] [[aliphatic]] [[hydrocarbon]]s (C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>18</sub>) found in [[petroleum]], especially an [[iso-octane]] 2,2,4 trimethyl-pentane; they are used as [[fuel]]s and [[solvent]]s

